Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:03.05,屏幕字4,,0,1518,250,,{\p1\c&HB3C3D0&\fscx400\fscy1\3c&H5241C8&\pos(1740,616)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
