Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:03.05,屏幕字4,,0,1518,250,,{\p1\c&HB3C3D0&\fscx300\fscy1\3c&H5241C8&\pos(1636,814)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:03.05,屏幕字4,,0,1518,250,,{\p1\c&HB3C3D0&\fscx500\fscy1\3c&H5241C8&\pos(1840,666)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
